Invocation Name: divine office magnificat
des: Pray Mary's Magnificat. Mary prayed her Magnificat when she visited her cousin Elizabeth. Marys Magnificat can be found in the Gospel of Luke, Chapter 1. This version of Mary’s Magnificat is from the Divine Office, which priests and deacons pray each day.
